  <brief_title>Immunophenotyping of Patients With Postoperative SIRS</brief_title>
  <official_title>Immunophenotyping of Patients Undergoing Open Heart Surgery to Assess Their Susceptibility of Developing a Systemic Inflammatory Response Syndrome (SIRS)</official_title>
